narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: As long as you have a supportive advisor (which I absolutely did), ENGL 489 is what you make of it. For me, the freedom to pursue my own writing that the project offered me was a wonderful experience, and I was able to structure it in a way that suited my needs.
Entirely what you make of it.
Take it if you know you can work on your own. But really, it's a dream to write what you want to write.
I found the experience of working on an extended project invaluable.
